{"tid":1789401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【聖誕佳節】Party Room渡節日、酒樓冬至飯預訂有冷暖","createTime":"2019-12-19T10:30:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T10:41:05.000Z","uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"51802da2992c66251f0ea28b613b321e807cd058","tid":1789401,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:30:21.000Z","msg":"【Now財經台】還有一星期就到冬至及聖誕，餐務管理協會表示，近日社會局勢較穩定，生意較前幾個月有好轉，冬至飯的預訂漸漸追回去年水平。但有主力做年輕人生意的Party Room負責人指，年輕人沒心情慶祝，預計聖誕生意額跌近60%。<br />\n<br />\n冬至前這個周日，在太古的這間酒樓，晚市時間全場爆滿。這一個月催淚彈少了，市民都趁機會一家人吃飯舒舒氣。所謂「冬大過年」，這間酒樓冬至飯的預訂數量已經追回和去年相若，但市民消費信心未恢復，套餐價格都不敢加價。<br />\n<br />\n餐務管理協會會長楊位醒表示，在社會動盪情況下，這半年已有超過300間酒樓結業，雖然年底訂檯情況有好轉，但他擔心這個好消息來得太遲。<br />\n<br />\n有人歡喜有人愁，Simone是一間Party Room的老闆，生意有一半是來自年輕人。往年電腦上排滿的預訂，今年受到反修例運動影響，到現在仍然有不少空檔。Simone表示，生意不好的原因是受到反修例運動影響，年輕人都無心情在聖誕消費，生意只有去年的三分之一。<br />\n<br />\n老闆說聖誕節會有不少團體來開大型派對，因為人數眾多，都會打通房間讓他們使用，今年多是6至8人的小型派對，一間房已經夠用。他又指，社會問題非短時間可解決，對下年的生意不感樂觀。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.now.com/mobile/special/topics/13/article/554185/cat//0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.now.com%2Fmobile%2Fspecial%2Ftopics%2F13%2Farticle%2F554185%2Fcat%2F%2F0&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfEwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=bb81bf3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://finance.now.com/mobile/special/topics/13/article/554185/cat//0</a>"},{"pid":"ded7bac4cf20270dd4448cf5d46935bcd4eab306","tid":1789401,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:30:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1df2d12ed4e82c341c61c73b6cd3b9b6a821f7","tid":1789401,"uid":88940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:30:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">經濟攬炒！香港人果七千萬比人搞啊！佢老母仲OT成九億<br />\n1221<br />\n1224<br />\n1225<br />\n</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[行動宜家唔推幾時推？］平安夜 賀佢老母呀！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1789301\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1789301</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c18163983675d906fd2ce2519b57ee0eb0fa91de","tid":1789401,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:30:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c4ecf030a6d7f8a58c80686c63e6194d79ed9bc","tid":1789401,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:31:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23fe23577f05aa72e16a1cc565d2c8521dfe9fc6","tid":1789401,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:31:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66861103df89cb72a9dd3f4bbb392930f9d37154","tid":1789401,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:32:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc8ca7a433fb304e3fd2670c5bf511571da87d77","tid":1789401,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:34:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe47e916b2241505f629a49bd34c4549610e97f","tid":1789401,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:35:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2282d4c422d998c45a8b5e849278b3525d20e0d","tid":1789401,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:41:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}